data.description: If you're looking for great place to call home in Madison, GA then look no further! Walking through the front door of this home, you're greeted by a spacious living room, that's great for entertaining or unwinding after a long day. With the kitchen right off the living room, you can provide for guests, or grab a late night snack without missing a second of the entertainment. A huge primary bedroom features two closets and an updated bathroom, with a new walk-in shower. There are two bedrooms on the other side of the house, but the owners currently use one as a dining room, making either layout perfect for hosting. Stepping out the back door you'll find a porch with plenty of room to entertain. Two storage buildings provide a great place to store lawn care equipment or toys for for those who love to spend their time out in the massive yard. This home features tons of updates including new floors, a new roof, a new HVAC unit and an updated kitchen. Just 5 minutes from a boat ramp on Lake Oconee, 8 Minutes to downtown Madison, and a few miles from I20, you can take full advantage of what the area has to offer. Call today to schedule a tour of this lovingly maintained home.
